The measure aims to achieve a two-sided effect, consisting, on one side, in increase of the degree of
_x000D_utilization of more environmentally friendly modes of transport and, on the other side, in the creation of
_x000D_favorable conditions for increasing the added value of transport activity with overall reduction of transport
_x000D_costs per unit of GDP.
_x000D_The expected results of its implementation are:
_x000D_• more efficient use of rail and water transport;
_x000D_• development of transport schemes and technologies meeting contemporary requirements with regard to
_x000D_environment and climate;
_x000D_• increased coordination and integration of different transport modes;
_x000D_• lower cost for passenger and cargo transport;
_x000D_• integration of the Bulgarian transport system with that of the EU and increasing its competitiveness.

