The programme financially supports energy savings, the increase of energy effectiveness and the use of renewable energy sources. It is a cross-cutting plan at a national level with sectorial structure; the target areas are the state administration and local governments, private sector, households and NGO’s

_x000D_This programme also provides information on energy efficiency issues (guidebooks, seminars, energy efficiency consulting centres etc.

_x000D_In detail the program supports the following activities:
_x000D_• Measures to reduce the energy intensity of public street lighting;
_x000D_• the reconstruction of a heating system and the heat generation in a building;
_x000D_• energy consulting provided by energy consulting and information centres;
_x000D_• courses and seminars about the energy sector;
_x000D_• publications, guides and informative materials about the energy sector;
_x000D_• the introduction of an energy management system;
_x000D_• the preparation of energy-saving projects financed using the EPC method.

